T02D1593:112b-1: shr'i badzra yo gi n'i s'a dha na n'a ma /
T02D1593:112b-3: dpal rdo rje rnal 'byor ma'i sgrub thabs zhes bya ba /
T02D1593:112b-4: dpal rdo rje rnal 'byor ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1593:112b-5: dpal ldan bde mchog thabs kyi gtso //
T02D1593:112b-6: gnyis med shes rab 'khor lor bcas //
T02D1593:112b-7: gus btud dpal ldan rnal 'byor ma'i //
T02D1593:112b-8: sgrub thabs rim pa bri bar bya //
T02D1593:112b-9: dang ldan dbang dang dam tshig ldan //
T02D1593:112b-10: sgrub la dpa' ba'i sngags pa yis //
T02D1593:112b-11: dur khrod la sogs dben pa'i gnas //
T02D1593:112b-12: nyams dgar mchod pa'i rten bzhugs la //
T02D1593:112b-13: stan bde ba la 'dug sems bya //
T02D1593:112b-14: lhag pa'i lhar bsam hr'i: 'od las //
T02D1593:112b-15: bla ma dkyil 'khor spyan drangs la //
T02D1593:112b-16: phyag dang mchod pa sngon 'gro bas //
T02D1593:112b-17: sdig pa bshags pa la sogs bya //
T02D1593:112b-18: de rjes tshangs pa'i gnas bzhi bsgom ;
T02D1593:112b-19: / kun kyang stong nyid rang bzhin bsam //
T02D1593:112b-20: sngags 'dis brtan pa nyid du bya //
T02D1593:112b-21: aom sva bh'a ba shuddha: sarbba dharmm'a:sva bh'a ba shoddho& ham /
T02D1593:112b-22: slar yang ye shes ngo bor bstan //
T02D1593:112b-23: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a ba a'atma ko& ham /
T02D1593:112b-24: zhes bya rang bzhin dag pa las //
T02D1593:112b-25: pam las padma nyi dkyil du //
T02D1593:112b-26: ae yi rnam pa'i cha byad can //
T02D1593:112b-27: lha mo khams gsum kun las 'das //
T02D1593:112b-28: dmigs pa rgya che gzhal yas khang //
T02D1593:112b-29: sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bor bsgom //
T02D1593:112b-30: de yi lte bar chos 'byung bsam //
T02D1593:112b-31: padma nyi ma ro stengs su //
T02D1593:112b-32: hr'i: yig byu ru dmar po 'dra //
T02D1593:112b-33: 'od zer spro bsdus slar bsams te //
T02D1593:112b-34: zhal gnyis phyag gnyis gar stabs bzhugs //
T02D1593:112b-35: dza ba sindhu ra yi mdog / g-yas pas gri gug nam mkhar gdengs //
T02D1593:112b-36: de bzhin gzhan gyis ka p'a la //
T02D1593:112b-37: kha tv'am gis brgyan rnam par 'dzin //
T02D1593:112b-38: g-yas pa phag gdong mkha' la spyod //
T02D1593:113a-1: shos khro mo'i zhal du bstan //
T02D1593:113a-2: phyag rgya'i rim pas sku lus mdzes //
T02D1593:113a-3: mgo bo'i do shal rgyan dang ldan //
T02D1593:113a-4: gar dgu'i ro ldan bsam par bya //
T02D1593:113a-5: yi ge gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs //
T02D1593:113a-6: lte ba snying ga mgrin pa dang //
T02D1593:113a-7: dpral ba spyi gtsug yan lag la //
T02D1593:113a-8: rim par sngags 'di bsam par bya //
T02D1593:113a-14: go cha bgos te ye shes bstim //
T02D1593:113a-15: dbang bskur mchod cing bstod pa bya //
T02D1593:113a-16: skyo na sngags 'di bzlas par bya //
T02D1593:113a-17: aom aom aom sarba buddha d'a ki n'i ye badzra
T02D1593:113a-18: warnna n'i ye h'um h'um h'um phat phat phat sv'a
T02D1593:113a-19: h'a / de rjes gto ra mas mchod par bya //
T02D1593:113a-20: lte bar chos kyi 'byung gnas bsam //
T02D1593:113a-22: steng nas g-yo ba'i rlung dgug cing //
T02D1593:113a-24: rnam par rtog pa rlung drod kyi //
T02D1593:113a-26: mar me la sogs rtags rnams 'byung //
T02D1593:113a-27: des skyo phyi nang lha mchod la //
T02D1593:113a-28: bstod cing dge ba bsngo bar bya //
T02D1593:113a-29: bdag gis sgrub thabs bris pa las //
T02D1593:113a-30: dge ba gang yod mdun byas te //
T02D1593:113a-32: lam nas byang chub 'gro bar shog / dpal rdo rje rnal 'byor ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02D1593:113a-33: rje d'i pam ka ra shr'i dzny'a nas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
